implicit wait -- 5 seconds time out --> It will wait for the element for 5 second and then it will monitor.

how to write implicit wait :
	-- After driver object is created we need to declare implicit wait.
	Ex: 
	WebDriver driver = new ChromeDriver();
	driver.manage().timeouts().implicitlyWait(Duration.ofSeconds(5));

	// that is globally defined so where ever locator is not visible it wait for 5 sec.

